Changes:

v1.0

   28 Jul 93: Initial version of ProMeter.
   29 Jul 93: NEW: Added menus: About, Quit
   30 Jul 93: NEW: Added menus: Select Color, Select Danger Color.
   30 Jul 93: NEW: Drew ProMeter-icon.
   31 Jul 93: NEW: Added menu: Save Settings.
   31 Jul 93: CHG: Made ProMeter font-sensitive.
    2 Aug 93: CHG: Made ProMeter also load settings when started from CLI.
    3 Aug 93: NEW: Added keyboard shortcuts: ESC, R(emember), D(ifference).
    3 Aug 93: NEW: Added 'Show as Kilobytes'-option in settingsmenu.
    3 Aug 93: NEW: Added 'Total gained:' in difference-string.
    4 Aug 93: CHG: Changed strings a bit.
    9 Aug 93: NEW: Added 'Jump to next screen'-option.
   10 Aug 93: CHG: Optimized code. Saved about 1000 bytes.

v1.1

   25 Aug 93: CHG: Kicked GadToolsBox sourcecode and Written my own. This was
	           done to be compatible with kick3.0 and GadToolsBox made the
	           window way to big with large fonts.
   28 Aug 93: NEW: Added ShowAsKiloBytes Tooltype. (Also saved with settings)
   28 Aug 93: CHG: Used NewLookMenus to look nicer on kick3.0.
   25 Sep 93: FIX: Fixed bug if no fastmem available. Crashed before due to
   	           division by zero.

v1.2 (First release)

    8 Apr 94: CHG: Optimized code, saved about 200 bytes.
    8 Apr 94: FIX: 184 bytes where lost when screenjumping
    8 Apr 94: NEW: Added Menu-option iconify.
    8 Apr 94: CHG: Difference gadget is now always enabled.
    8 Apr 94: CHG: Screen pops to front when jumping.
    8 Apr 94: CHG: Window activates when openened.
    9 Apr 94: NEW: Drew ProMeter-MWB-icon.

@EndNode

